<view class="page" wx:if="{{detail}}">
  <view class="header">
    <image class="header-bg" src="{{detail.poi.image}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
    <view class="header-mask"></view>
    <view class="header-nav" bindtap="navigateBack">
      <image class="icon-back" src="/imgs/back.svg"></image>
    </view>
    <view class="header-content">
      <view class="label">Trip 门票分销</view>
      <view class="poi-name">{{detail.poi.name}}</view>
      <view class="poi-reason">{{detail.poi.reason}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="ticket-title">{{detail.title}}</view>
    <view class="price-row">
      <view class="price">{{detail.priceType === 'reference' ? '参考价 ' : ''}}¥{{detail.price}}</view>
      <view class="origin">{{detail.priceType === 'reference' ? '原价参考 ' : ''}}¥{{detail.originalPrice}}</view>
      <view class="score">转化 {{detail.conversionScore}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="status-row">
      <view class="status-badge status-{{detail.ticketStatus}}">{{statusLabelMap[detail.ticketStatus] || detail.ticketStatus}}</view>
      <view class="mode-badge">{{purchaseModeLabelMap[detail.purchaseTarget.purchaseMode] || 'Trip 承接页'}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="benefit-list">
      <block wx:for="{{detail.benefits}}" wx:key="*this">
        <view class="benefit">{{item}}</view>
      </block>
    </view>
    <view class="body-text subtle">适合人群：{{detail.suitableFor || detail.audience}}</view>
    <view class="body-text subtle">价格类型：{{detail.priceType === 'reference' ? '目录参考价，最新价格以下单页为准' : '实时价'}}</view>
    <view class="body-text subtle">价格更新时间：{{detail.priceUpdatedAt || detail.lastUpdated}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-title">推荐理由</view>
    <view class="body-text">{{detail.poi.reason}}</view>
    <view class="tag-row">
      <block wx:for="{{detail.poi.tags}}" wx:key="*this">
        <view class="tag">{{item}}</view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel bottom-space">
    <view class="section-title">购买说明</view>
    <view class="body-text">{{detail.bookingNote}}</view>
    <view class="body-text subtle" wx:if="{{stale}}">当前内容来自最近一次计划快照；如需更新价格参考，请返回结果页下拉刷新。</view>
    <view class="body-text subtle">当前承接方式：{{purchaseModeLabelMap[detail.purchaseTarget.purchaseMode] || 'Trip 承接页'}}。</view>
    <view class="body-text subtle">失败兜底：{{detail.purchaseTarget.reason}}</view>
    <view class="body-text subtle">点击按钮后会前往 Trip 查看最新价格并预订；若目标页缺失或打开失败，会自动回退到可打开的 Trip 承接页，不会出现空白页。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="bottom-bar">
    <view>
      <view class="bottom-price">{{detail.priceType === 'reference' ? '参考价 ' : ''}}¥{{detail.price}}</view>
      <view class="bottom-sub">{{statusLabelMap[detail.ticketStatus] || detail.ticketStatus}} · {{detail.priceType === 'reference' ? '最新价格以下单页为准' : 'Trip 实时价'}}</view>
    </view>
    <button class="buy-btn" bindtap="buyTicket" disabled="{{detail.purchaseTarget.purchaseMode === 'disabled'}}">{{detail.purchaseTarget.buttonText || detail.cta}}</button>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="empty-page" wx:elif="{{!loading}}">
  <view class="empty-card">
    <view class="section-title">未找到门票信息</view>
    <view class="body-text">当前缺少可展示的门票详情，请返回结果页重新选择，或切换到支持城市继续体验。</view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="empty-page" wx:else>
  <view class="empty-card">
    <view class="section-title">门票详情加载中</view>
    <view class="body-text">正在刷新最新票券信息，请稍候。</view>
  </view>
</view>
